about.description: A set of helpers for baking your Django site out as flat files
about.summary: A set of helpers for baking your Django site out as flat files

name: django-bakery
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "django-bakery" %}
{% set version = "0.12.7" %}
{% set sha256 = "48156dbd9ddb762bef4352350a5f43744740529148fd70598120d8d2ae5e273c" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - django
    - six >1.5.2
    - boto3 >=1.4.4
    
test:
  imports:
    - bakery

about:
  home: https://github.com/datadesk/django-bakery
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENSE'
  summary: 'A set of helpers for baking your Django site out as flat files'
  description: |
    A set of helpers for baking your Django site out as flat files
  doc_url: https://django-bakery.readthedocs.io/en/latest/
  dev_url: https://github.com/datadesk/django-bakery

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - cshaley
    - sannykr
